{
  "stem": "24111.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My mother got-- got almost all her things back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But on the way of crossing, everything was lost.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "A day or two later-- oh, I forgot to tell you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The Swiss police or the-- the Swiss military forces in-- on the-- on the side of Ponte [?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Tresa ?] informed the authorities.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they knew, because of Dr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Lichtheim, that this group is coming, or will-- will eventually come.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And now we are here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all the children and the few adults which came with them were interned.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And my mother was interned in Montreux.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it took a while that the-- till the Jewish community could organize a building and facilities for suddenly for 100 children.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were unexpected, and there was nothing like that ever happened in Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were able to get in a large building in [FRENCH], which is in-- in the vicinity of Montreux in the canton of [FRENCH] in Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all the children and Joschko and my mother and Mr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Avien, ?] they are united there, and they really started the same hachshara-- the same [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] learning facilities they tried to have years before up to-- to this point, also in Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How did you make contact with them?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in Busserach.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Dr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Lichtheim sent me sometimes a few francs, six francs, five francs, into the camp and also notes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In a [? month, ?] I got a letter from my mother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you can imagine what that meant to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She-- he knew--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--of her.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He knew about me, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when he made contact, he sent me the-- the note.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, he also let Joschko know where we are.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
